TextEng: I want to try the combat drills, Sir!
I don't want to try the combat drills, Sir!
Text: 전투 훈련은 하고 싶지 않습니다, 교관님!

TextEng: Me want do combat drills, Sir!
Text: 나 전투 훈련 하고 싶어, 교관님!

TextEng: Me no want do combat drills, Sir!
Text: 나 전투 훈련 하기 싫어, 교관님!

TextEng: Sir! I'm ready, Sir!
Sir, no Sir! I'm not ready yet, Sir!
Text: 교관님, 아닙니다, 교관님! 아직 준비 안 됐습니다, 교관님!

TextEng: Sir! Me ready, Sir!
Sir, me not ready, Sir!
Text: 교관님, 나 준비 안 됐어, 교관님!

TextEng: All right, let's get this over with.
What's with all the shouting? Is this supposed to inspire me or something?
Text: 왜 그렇게 소리 지르는 거죠? 이게 저한테 영감을 주는 건가요?

TextEng: Okay, me do it. Hurry up.
Why you be so mean?
I don't have time for this nonsense.
Me not got time for this.
I'm ready to continue my training, Sir!
I want to ask you some questions, Sir.
Me ready for continue training, Sir!
Me want ask you questions, Sir.
I think I'll be going now, Sir.
Text: 이제 가봐야 할 것 같습니다, 교관님.

TextEng: Me want go now, Sir.
Sir! Yes, Sir!
Sir! No, Sir! Please repeat the information, Sir!
Text: 교관님! 아닙니다, 교관님! 다시 말씀해 주십시오, 교관님!

TextEng: Sir, no, Sir! Me need you repeat, Sir!
Text: 교관님, 아니야, 교관님! 나 다시 말해줘, 교관님!

TextEng: Yeah, yeah, I get it, already.
Yeah, yeah, me get it already.
Sir! Yes, Sir!
Sir! Please repeat, Sir!
I got it. Let's move this show along.
Me got it. Hurry and finish talk. You boring.
Text: 나 알았어. 빨리 끝내. 너 지루해.

TextEng: Sir! Yes, Sir!
Sir! Please repeat, Sir
Oh, it's clear. Real loud and real clear. On a side note, what's up with your breath?
Text: 아, 명확합니다. 정말 크고 명확하죠. 그런데 입 냄새는 뭐죠?

TextEng: You clear. You also loud and have stinky breath.
Text: 명확해. 목소리 크고 입 냄새 나.

TextEng: I think I'll pass.
Me pass.
I'm tired of calling you "Sir." How about we compromise and I call you "Shirley?"
Text: 교관님이라고 부르는 건 지겨워요. 타협해서 셜리라고 부르는 건 어때요?

TextEng: Me not want call you Sir no more. Me want call you Shirley.
Text: 나 교관님 부르기 싫어. 나 셜리라고 부를래.

TextEng: Sir! Yes, Sir!
Sir! Please repeat, Sir!
Yeah, yeah. I've got it. No need to shout and holler.
Text: 네, 네. 알겠어요. 소리 지르고 고함칠 필요 없어요.

TextEng: Me got it. You not need shout so much.
Text: 나 알았어. 너 그렇게 소리 안 질러도 돼.

TextEng: I already know everything I need to about combat!
Text: 전투에 대해 필요한 건 이미 다 알아요!

TextEng: Me already know what me need 'bout combat!
Text: 나 전투에 대해 필요한 거 이미 다 알아!

TextEng: Not interested.
Sir! I wish to hear your combat tutorial, Sir!
Text: 교관님! 전투 설명을 듣고 싶습니다, 교관님!

TextEng: Sir! Me want hear you tutorial!
Text: 교관님! 나 당신 튜토리얼 듣고 싶어!

TextEng: Me wants to get to combat trial test things.
Text: 나 전투 시험 시련 거 하고 싶어.

TextEng: I just want to get to the combat trials.
Me needs yous to go over basic stuff.
Text: 나 너한테 기본 것들 다시 들어야 해.

TextEng: I need you to go over basic training.
Me finished! What nows?
I have completed my training. What now, sir?
